<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9613</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15232</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森不能集中精力。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15232</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17948</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他甚至不能走路。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17948</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20926</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的腿太痒了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20926</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25493</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>昨天晚上，他和爸爸在户外吃晚餐。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25493</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31872</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们回室内后，贾森的身上全是蚊子咬的包。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31872</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34909</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他很痒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34909</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41691</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我受不了了！” 贾森把腿上的包给大家看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41691</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47259</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇。” 尼娜说，“看上去很痒。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47259</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51792</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你应该用驱蚊水的。” 莉琪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51792</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56139</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我用不了驱蚊水。” 贾森说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56139</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59276</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么？” 尼娜问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59276</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65737</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“因为我对化学药品过敏。” 贾森皱着眉头说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65737</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70695</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那你今天真幸运！” 邓恩老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70696</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73956</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“幸运？” 贾森说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73956</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77073</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“被蚊子咬有什么幸运的？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77074</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们今天要做驱蚊水。” 邓恩老师解释说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87774</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是一种天然的驱蚊水。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87774</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94371</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真的吗？” 贾森不敢相信，“怎么做呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94371</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97825</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“邓恩老师是一名化学老师。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97825</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100456</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他会给我们解释的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100456</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105596</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>对吗，邓恩老师？” 波比看着老师。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105596</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118337</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。” 邓恩老师点了点头，“坐下吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118337</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124390</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里有些瓶子里是非常浓的油，叫精油。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124390</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129833</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>混合几种精油，就能做出赶走蚊子的气味儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129833</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133947</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>邓恩老师清了清嗓子，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133947</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137114</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是说，让蚊子飞走。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137115</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139567</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜咯咯笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139567</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143769</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她喜欢邓恩老师的小幽默。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143770</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148409</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“气味儿会不会很难闻？” 伊坦问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148409</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150056</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“应该不会。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150056</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>等一下你们就会知道了。” 邓恩老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154569</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158553</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“每个人都拿一个喷水瓶，写上名字。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158553</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164713</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这就是你自己的驱蚊水瓶。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164713</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169042</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森小心地写上自己的名字。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169042</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175620</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“首先，我们要加基础油。” 邓恩老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175620</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179183</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天我们的基础油是橄榄油。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179183</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184051</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>先加基础油，精油才不会太浓。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184051</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188466</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“而且不容易过敏，对吗？” 贾森问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188466</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196158</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对。有的人会因为精油太浓长小红点儿。” 邓恩老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196158</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201138</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“所以我们要仔细测量精油的量。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201138</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> 大家把橄榄油倒进去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接着，邓恩老师拿起一个瓶子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210953</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看到这个瓶子的特殊盖子了吗？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213917</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这个滴管可以一滴一滴地测量桉树油。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223616</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>邓恩老师滴了几滴在自己手上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223616</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229542</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他搓了搓手，让孩子们闻。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229542</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233096</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我喜欢这个气味。” 莉琪说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233096</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235720</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“闻上去很清新。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235720</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237761</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>伊坦闻了闻。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237761</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241615</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇！气味儿真浓。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241616</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246505</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“滴二十滴到你的瓶子里。” 邓恩老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246505</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249796</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森眯了眯眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249796</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254821</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得它会刺激我的眼睛。” 他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254821</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它确实会刺激你的眼睛！” 邓恩老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267110</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“所以一定要小心，弄完精油后不要碰自己的眼睛。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267110</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271322</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“接下来放什么呢？” 波比问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271322</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277562</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>邓恩老师拿起另一个瓶子。“香茅精油。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277562</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282093</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们家后院有香茅蜡烛。” 尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282093</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288423</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“香茅可以驱蚊。” 邓恩老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288423</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293089</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“所以，这个也加二十滴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>293089</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296328</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>摇一摇，就做好了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296328</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301799</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>下次出去的时候，可以喷在胳膊和腿上。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301799</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>305870</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“贾森，今晚出去的时候可以试试。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>305870</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>310872</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>应该没有蚊子咬你了。” 邓恩老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>310872</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>314745</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会试试的。” 贾森说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>314745</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>325719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，我已经没有地方让蚊子咬了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>